PP/Al2O3 + MD comparison) is highly niche. The current results suggest this specific combination might not exist exactly as described, or requires deeper academic digging.\n\n3.  **Decompose Research Question:**\n    *   Q1: Does experimental evidence exist for DVS crosslinked PEI coatings?\n    *   Q2: Are these coatings applied to plasma-activated polypropylene (PP)?\n    *   Q3: Are these coatings applied to aluminum oxide (Al2O3)?\n    *   Q4: What are the measured peel or lap-shear adhesion strengths?\n    *   Q5: Do molecular dynamics (MD) predictions exist for this system?\n    *   Q6: How do experimental values compare to MD single-bond work of adhesion predictions?\n\n    *   *Status:* All sub-questions have ZERO evidence so far. The read pages are irrelevant to the specific chemistry/substrate combo.\n\n4.  **Identify Contradictions:**\n    *   None yet. Not enough data.\n\n5.  **Ident Knowledge Gaps:**\n    *   Specific adhesion values (N/m or MPa).\n    *   Existence of MD simulations for PEI-DVS interfaces.\n    *   Existence of plasma treatment protocols for PP/Al2O3 in this context.\n    *   Direct comparison studies (Experiment vs. Simulation).\n\n6.  **Perspectives Needed:**\n    *   Scientific (primary literature), Methodological (how adhesion was measured/simulated).\n\n7.  **Draft Queries:**\n    *   Need to target academic databases (even via web search) and specific chemical combinations.\n    *   Web: \"divinyl sulfone polyethylenimine adhesion strength\", \"PEI DVS crosslinked coating polypropylene plasma\", \"molecular dynamics simulation PEI adhesion work of adhesion\".\n    *   Academic: \"divinyl sulfone\" AND \"polyethylenimine\" AND \"adhesion\" AND (\"simulation\" OR \"molecular dynamics\"), \"lap shear\" AND \"polyethylenimine\" AND \"crosslinked\".\n    *   Exa: Semantic search for the specific comparison (experiment vs MD).\n\n8.  **Assess Completeness:**\n    *   Status: 'expanding'. Major sub-questions unanswered.\n    *   Evidence Strength: All weak/non-existent.\n\n9.  **Continuation:**\n    *   Yes, definitely need to continue. The current results are off-target (regulatory vs. scientific).\n\n10. **Construct JSON:**\n    *   Ensure strict JSON validity. Escape quotes. No trailing commas.\n    *   Follow the implied schema based on the prompt's numbered list (though the prompt asks for JSON *containing* the answers to 1-10, I need to structure it logically).\n    *   *Self-Correction on Schema:* The prompt asks me to respond with valid JSON only. It lists 10 tasks. I should structure the JSON keys to reflect these tasks clearly.\n    *   Keys: `sub_questions`, `contradictions`, `knowledge_gaps`, `confidence_rating`, `perspectives_needed`, `web_queries`, `academic_queries`, `exa_queries`, `answer_completeness`, `continue_searching`.\n\n    *   *Refining Content:*\n        *   `sub_questions`: List the decomposition and their status.\n        *   `contradictions`: Empty list or note none found.\n        *   `knowledge_gaps`: Specific factual questions.\n        *   `confidence_rating`: \"LOW\".\n        *   `perspectives_needed`: [\"Scientific\", \"Methodological\"].\n        *   `web_queries`: Targeted strings.\n        *   `academic_queries`: Boolean strings.\n        *   `exa_queries`: Natural language.\n        *   `answer_completeness`: Status and details.\n        *   `continue_searching`: Boolean.\n\n    *   *Constraint Check:* \"No prose, no markdown, no code fences — just the JSON object.\"\n    *   *Warning:* I must not include ```json ... ``` blocks. Just the raw JSON text.\n\n    *   *Drafting the JSON content:*\n        *   Make sure to escape newlines if any (better to avoid newlines in strings for safety).\n        *   Ensure all keys are quoted.\n        *   Ensure no comments.\n\n    *   *Specific focus:* The current search results are heavily regulatory. I need to pivot hard to academic/scientific literature. The specific combination (DVS/PEI/Plasma/PP/Al2O3/MD) is very specific. It's possible the exact combination doesn't exist, and I need to find proximate evidence (e.g., PEI on PP, DVS crosslinking elsewhere, MD of PEI interfaces).\n\n    *   *Refining Queries:*\n        *   \"polyethylenimine divinyl sulfone crosslinking adhesion test\"\n        *   \"plasma treated polypropylene polyethylenimine coating adhesion\"\n        *   \"molecular dynamics simulation polyethylenimine substrate adhesion\"\n        *   \"work of adhesion PEI aluminum oxide simulation\"\n        *   \"lap shear strength PEI coating experimental\"\n\n    *   *Refining Gaps:*\n        *   \"What is the specific lap shear strength (MPa) of DVS-PEI on plasma-PP?\"\n        *   \"Are there MD simulations calculating work of adhesion for PEI-DVS networks?\"\n        *   \"Is there a direct study comparing experimental peel strength to MD predictions for this system?\"\n\n    *   *Confidence:* LOW. Only 3 generic pages read.\n\n    *   *Completeness:* \"expanding\".\n\n    *   *Continue:* true.\n\n    *   *Formatting:* Ensure valid JSON.\n\n    *   *Final Check:* The prompt says \"You MUST respond with valid JSON only. No prose, no markdown, no code fences — just the JSON object.\" I will output the raw JSON string.\n\n    *   *Structure:*\n        {\n          \"sub_questions_analysis\": [...],\n          \"contradictions\": [...],\n          \"knowledge_gaps\": [...],\n          \"confidence_rating\": \"...\",\n          \"confidence_reasoning\": \"...\",\n          \"perspectives_needed\": [...],\n          \"web_queries\": [...],\n          \"academic_queries\": [...],\n          \"exa_queries\": [...],\n          \"answer_completeness\": { ... },\n          \"continue_searching\": true\n        }\n\n    *   *Wait, one more check:* The prompt asks me to \"Decompose...\", \"What CONTRADICTIONS...\", \"What specific KNOWLEDGE GAPS...\", etc. I should map these to JSON keys clearly.\n\n    *   *Let's build the JSON.*\n    *   Escape characters: Double quotes inside strings must be escaped.\n    *   No newlines in the actual output string (except within JSON string values if escaped, but better to keep single line or properly formatted JSON block without markdown fences). Actually, standard JSON allows whitespace. I will format it nicely but without markdown fences.\n\n    *   *Wait, instruction:* \"No prose, no markdown, no code fences — just the JSON object.\"\n    *   This means I cannot write ```json ... ```. I must start with `{` and end with `}`.\n\n    *   *Content Check:* The current results are terrible for the specific question. I need to acknowledge that the specific combination might be novel or non-existent, requiring proximate searches.\n\n    *   *Sub-questions:*\n        1. Existence of DVS-PEI adhesive coatings? (Weak/None)\n        2. Application on plasma-activated PP? (Weak/None)\n        3. Application on Al2O3? (Weak/None)\n        4. Measured peel/lap-shear strengths? (Weak/None)\n        5. MD predictions of single-bond work of adhesion? (Weak/None)\n        6. Comparison between experiment and MD? (Weak/None)\n\n    *   *Gaps:* All of them.\n\n    *   *Queries:* Need to be sharper.\n\n    *   *Okay, ready to generate.*\n","input_tokens":1439,"output_tokens":3112,"reasoning_tokens":2165,"duration_ms":49478.90489999554,"cost_usd":0.005229},{"ts":"2026-03-12T02:02:23.750201+00:00","vid":"WEB_20260312T015506_435334","node":"structured","type":"llm_detail","call_type":"structured:PageSummaryBatch","model":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-02-15","temperature":0.5,"max_tokens":8192,"reasoning_enabled":false,"response_format":"","prompt_messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You MUST respond with valid JSON only. No prose, no markdown, no code fences — just the JSON object."},{"role":"user","content":"You are a research analyst reading web pages for a deep research project.\n\nRESEARCH QUESTION: What experimental evidence exists for divinyl sulfone (DVS) crosslinked polyethylenimine\n  (PEI/BPEI) adhesive coatings on plasma-activated polypropylene and aluminum oxide\n  substrates, and how do measured peel or lap-shear adhesion strengths compare with molecular\n  dynamics predictions of single-bond work of adhesion?\n\nRead the following 4 pages and create a research note for each.\n\n--- PAGE: The Performance of Crosslinking with Divinyl Sulfone as ... ---\nURL: https://www.researchgate.net/publication/276236669_The_Performance_of_Crosslinking_with_Divinyl_Sulfone_as_Controlled_by_the_Interplay_Between_the_Chemical_Modification_and_Conformation_of_Hyaluronic_Acid\nCONTENT:\n[ ](https://www.researchgate.net) # Security check required We've detected unusual activity from your network. To continue, complete the security check below. 驗證成功。正在等待 www.researchgate.net 回應 Ray ID: 9daf33285f413e7c Client IP: 216.232.201.117 © 2008-2026 ResearchGate GmbH. All rights reserved.\n\n--- PAGE: Crosslinking Approaches for Polyethylene Imine (PEI) and ... ---\nURL: https://www.mdpi.com/2076-3417/15/9/4767\nCONTENT:\n(https://www.mdpi.com/2076-3417/15/9/4767#main) [![MDPI](https://mdpi-res.com/cdn-cgi/image/w=56,h=30/https://mdpi-res.com/data/mdpi-logo-black.svg)![MDPI](https://mdpi-res.com/cdn-cgi/image/w=70,h=56/https://mdpi-res.com/data/mdpi-logo-black.svg)](https://www.mdpi.com/) * Journals * [All Journals](https://www.mdpi.com/about/journals) * [Journal Finder](https://www.mdpi.com/about/journalfinder) * [Proceedings Series](https://www.mdpi.com/about/proceedings) * [Propose a Journal](https://www.mdpi.com/about/journals/proposal) * Topics By Subjects * [Biology & Life Sciences](https://www.mdpi.com/topics?facets=NobwRAlgJmBcYGcCuAjAVgUwMYBcFgBowA3AQwBskM4wBGQsc0lDcmgIQgHtyuBzAJ4ACAGRCAMhABmGIQGUsEDADssGfAF8AukA) * [Business & Economics](https://www.mdpi.com/topics?facets=NobwRAlgJmBcYGcCuAjAVgUwMYBcFgBowA3AQwBskM4wAmQsc0lDcmgISQQgDsMEEAAgBkggKJYA9j0kBbCFnwBfALpA) * [Chemistry & Materials](https://www.mdpi.com/topics?facets=NobwRAlgJmBcYGcCuAjAVgUwMYBcFgBowA3AQwBskM4wBmQsc0lDcmgYQAsMBbCBHACcAngAI